        <abstract>
            <p>Glad GHD goes on with ripple-marks; if he makes out a theory of ripples, they might give important information about the most ancient deposits.</p> 
<p>CD has been wonderfully glorified in the <hi rend="italic">Times</hi> [review of <hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi>, 20 Nov 1880].</p> 
        </abstract>
